rows.label: qst001901_msg0001
rows.name: Y-you really gathered them all, mo?!

rows.label: qst001901_msg0002
rows.name:
I thought I'd never make
it in time, mo. You saved
me, mo, you saved me!

rows.label: qst001901_msg0003
rows.name: How can I ever thank you...

rows.label: qst001901_msg0004
rows.name:
That's it, mo! I'll give you
the reward for this job!

rows.label: qst001901_msg0005
rows.name:
I was able to complete this
job thanks to you, so please
don't worry about it, mo.

rows.label: qst001901_msg0006
rows.name:
The client, Jambhar, is
in the Cargo Transportation
Zone in Superbia, mo.

rows.label: qst001901_msg0007
rows.name:
I'll leave it to you to collect
the reward in my place, mo.

rows.label: qst001901_msg0008
rows.name:
I never want to see that horrible man
who tormented Sekaka, the Mushroom-Feast
Salvager, ever again, mo...

rows.label: qst001901_msg0009
rows.name:
Well then, I'll leave the rest to
you, mo. Thank you so much, mo.
